<h1>Injury chart</h1>
<p>If a warrior is taken out of action in a game they must roll on the injury chart to see what fate has befallen them!
You can choose for Henchmen to just roll on the Henchmen injury instead or use the more detailed Hero chart.</p>
<p>
<h3>Henchmen Injury Chart</h3>
Roll a D6:<br>
<br>
<div><b>D6 Dice roll generation</b></div>
<div><i>refresh page to reset</i></div>
<div><% localRoll =  expRoll() %></div>
<div>Roll 1: <%= localRoll["roll1"] %></div>
<br>
<strong>1-2</strong>: Dead <br>
<strong>3-6</strong>: Alive and well
</p> <br>
<h3>Hero Injury Chart</h3>
<p>Roll a D6 to represent tens and a D6 to represent digits and consult the D66 Chart below</p>

